Brazil to Boost BNDES, Caixa Capital With Petrobras’s Shares

-- B y   F r a n c i s c o   M a r c e l i n o
-- 
2011-02-17T10:51:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-17/brazil-to-boost-bndes-caixa-capital-with-petrobras-s-shares.html
  Brazil ’s government authorized a
capital increase at the development bank, known as BNDES, and at
state-controllled bank Caixa Economica Federal, according to a
 decree  published in the nation’s Official Gazette today.  Brazil will increase BNDES’s capital by as much as 6.4
billion reais by transferring  Petroleo Brasileiro SA ’s shares
into the bank. The government will boost Caixa’s capital by as
much as 2.2 billion reais transferring Petrobras and Centrais
Eletricas Brasileiras stock into the lender.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Francisco Marcelino in Sao Paulo at 
 mdeoliveira@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Laura Price at 
 lprice3@bloomberg.net  